{"tid":338668,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS4機主討論區(11) 動漫節買機最抵！","createTime":"2017-07-28T11:11:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T07:26:31.000Z","uid":11402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d234556e00c90c5e79a825926b0d9a85e37cbda","tid":338668,"uid":11402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T11:11:15.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">LIHKG-PS4機主討論區</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o5d2H9Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo5d2H9Q.png&h=251dbe0a&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Welcome to PlayStation 4 Group.<br />\n歡迎加入PlayStation 4 大家庭。</span></strong><br />\n建議新加入的玩家首先細閱下文，如再有任何除購買主機以外的問題，歡迎提出。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有關購買主機之查詢，請到友Post查詢及討論。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">常見 Q &amp; A</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q1.</span> 我已經擁有PS4，使唔使轉PS4 Pro？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A1.</span> PS4 Pro於4.5 Version Firmware 更新中新增Boost 模式，可以提升運行舊Game性能，當然有部份遊戲無明顯作用：如對戰Game(因遊戲方多數會將遊戲設定tune到所有玩家在同樣設定，以達致平衡)，又如2D平面遊戲或AVG等遊戲內容。<br />\n整體上嚟講，PS4 Pro喺機能上和效果上都較舊版PS4或PS4 Slim優勝，個人建議如需增添多一部PS4的應該選PS4 Pro，當然輕度/休憩玩家或金錢上有困難則可選PS4 Slim。<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q2.</span> 我應唔應該換原裝HDD做SSD或SSHD？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A2.</span> 視乎你的金錢及對遊戲的要求，更換原裝HDD到SSD或SSHD只是對安裝遊戲和讀取遊戲時速度提升，並不會影響畫面質素。<br />\n<br />\n舊版PS4和PS4 Slim：SSD 快10% - 30% &gt; SSHD 快 5% - 10% &gt; 原裝HDD<br />\nPS4 Pro：SSD 快10% - 60% &gt;  SSHD 快 5%  - 30% &gt; 原裝HDD<br />\n得益於SATA III接口，在原裝HDD之下，使用較新接口的PS4 Pro快舊版PS4和PS4 Slim約 5% - 10%，所以在讀取遊戲速度上PS4 Pro更換後效果更明顯<br />\n(以上數值由各網上測試推斷而來，各款遊戲及使用的HDD/SSD/SSHD品牌差異都會造成明顯差距，請自行再Google相關的品牌測試)<br />\n<br />\n如果只單純想安裝更多遊戲，於4.5 Version Firmware更新後任何PS4都可以使用外置硬碟，可自行選擇購買內置硬碟更換還是買外置硬碟<br />\n<br />\n更換HDD只需拆PS4的HDD外殼部份並換走儲存裝置，正常裝拆並不影響主機保養<br />\n更換方式：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60596&amp;snA=25909\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D60596%26snA%3D25909&d=%2FlPv3t7WlvhdxvNzqqPsTleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=209b8ccd\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60596&amp;snA=25909</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q3.</span> PS4槍Game好難用，可唔可以用電腦Mouse 同Keyboard？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A3.</span> 當然可以，有兩個方法：1)用轉換器轉換電腦Mouse 同Keyboard 同 2)買第三方PS4專用Mouse 同Keyboard<br />\n方法1：轉換器如平價的Hori Tac4和ATEN PHANTOM-S，貴價的XIM4或Brook Sniper等，價格為500港元到1,200港元左右，但同樣由於是模擬手制，會出現延遲等問題<br />\n方法2：第三方PS4專用Mouse 同Keyboard如HORI 的TAC K1、M1和G1等，價格由500港元到1000港元左右。"},{"pid":"dcc8210fd90911b9ecf452a81a4525c13b008843","tid":338668,"uid":11402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T11:12:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Q7.</span> PS4用wifi定用LAN線直插線上網？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A7.</span> 首選LAN線，穩定好多<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q8.</span> 保養有無得加長？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A8.</span> 可以用官方價$298於藍店或Sony Shop購買加長保養卡，但保養加強服務只限PS4主機，不包括手制及其他配件如Camera及VR。<br />\n網上登記保養另外送90日保養服務，所以最長保養期為2年連90日。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q9.</span> 咩係藍店 <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A9.</span> 即係PlayStation Platinum Shop，<br />\n另有Sony Store和特許經銷商出售PS4及其遊戲<br />\n可以去下面網頁查詢各店舖位置<br />\n<a href=\"https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/support/retail-store/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.playstation.com%2Fcht-hk%2Fsupport%2Fretail-store%2F&d=%2FlPv3t7WlvhdxvNzqqPsTleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=f4792073\" target=\"_blank\">https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/support/retail-store/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q10.</span> 啱啱成為機主，點登記保養？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A10.</span> 由於Sony官網正進行更新維修，暫時無法提供網上登記。<br />\n<a href=\"https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/support/warranty-services/faq/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.playstation.com%2Fcht-hk%2Fsupport%2Fwarranty-services%2Ffaq%2F&d=%2FlPv3t7WlvhdxvNzqqPsTleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=5ed46bf0\" target=\"_blank\">https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/support/warranty-services/faq/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q11.</span> 幫部機換咗HDD，點裝返系統入去？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A11.</span> 請閱以下網址<br />\n<a href=\"https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/ps4/system-update/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.playstation.com%2Fcht-hk%2Fps4%2Fsystem-update%2F&d=%2FlPv3t7WlvhdxvNzqqPsTleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=8fd2420e\" target=\"_blank\">https://asia.playstation.com/cht-hk/ps4/system-update/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>主機簡介：</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nPlayStation&reg;4 (簡稱PS4)由Sony Interactive Entertainment LLC所推出，由2014年12月17日起在香港推出初代CUH-10XX系列PS4，到機能小改版的CUH-11XX系列PS4和改善部份問題的CUH-12XX系列PS4，更於2016年9月9日推出輕量改良型的CUH-20XX系列的PS4 Slim及同年11月9日推出加強型CUH-70XX系列的PS4 Pro。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不同系列主機：</span><br />\n<br />\nPS4 Pro與PS4 Slim熱賣中<br />\n<br />\n<strong>CUH-70XX系列PS4 Pro</strong>：機能大改進版本，尺寸增加至327 x 295 x 55mm，支援 4K 遊戲，亦支援 HDR 影片(所有型號的PS4主機均可由Firmware更新中(Software 4.0)升級到支援HDR。)；機背接頭除舊有的HDMI接口<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(由1.4a升位2.0b，其實是為4K畫面而升級，一般用家不用在意)</span>、有線網絡接口、PS4 Camera接口、光纖音訊S/PDIF Audio輸出接口外，更新增一組USB接口；以及WiFi升級為支援5GHz的IEEE 802.11ac規格，藍牙4.0，全部USB升級為USB3.1(Gen1)和硬碟提升到支援SATA III。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(需留意PS4 Pro只支援4K 遊戲，依舊不支援4K影片播放。)</span><br />\n官方建議售價：3,180港元 (1TB) <br />\n<br />\n<strong>CUH-20XX系列PS4 Slim</strong>：機能大致與CUH-1XXX系列相同，尺寸減少至約288 &times; 265 &times; 39 mm，同樣大幅度的為主機淨重、耗電量、熱量和噪音，並且WiFi方面升級為支援5GHz的IEEE 802.11ac規格及藍牙升級為4.0，USB也升級到USB3.1(Gen1)，但減少了光纖音訊S/PDIF Audio輸出接口，已取代舊系列。<br />\n官方建議售價：2,380港元 (500GB) 及2,680港元 (1TB)<br />\n<br />\nPS4 Slim有黑及白色機選擇。<br />\nPS4 Pro現只得黑色機可供選擇。"},{"pid":"ca054ad783f75fce2f32f8ab9160f812956410da","tid":338668,"uid":11402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T11:14:32.000Z","msg":"方法2：第三方PS4專用Mouse 同Keyboard如HORI 的TAC K1、M1和G1等，價格由500港元到1000港元左右。<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q4.</span> PSN 同PS Plus有咩關係？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A4.</span> PSN即係PlayStation&trade;Network，其實係由Sony PlayStation&trade;提供的個人帳戶，呢個帳戶在PS4上只用作分辨使用者從而使用其儲檔及設定。而一般玩家所以及的PlayStation&reg;Plus(部份人搞錯為PSN Plus，實為PS Plus)，是由Sony PlayStation&trade;提供的個人帳戶升級服務，當中包括多人線上遊玩，每月免費遊戲，優先預享特權以及自動下載更新及在線資料備份等等。<br />\n詳細有關PS Plus的介紹請往下面連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://asia.playstation.com/hk/cht/psn/psPlus#overiew\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.playstation.com%2Fhk%2Fcht%2Fpsn%2FpsPlus%23overiew&d=%2FlPv3t7WlvhdxvNzqqPsTleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=a947c0d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://asia.playstation.com/hk/cht/psn/psPlus#overiew</a><br />\n每月PS Plus所提供的免費遊戲及其他優惠可前往下面網頁下載：<br />\n<a href=\"https://store.playstation.com/#!/zh-hant-hk/home/%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2/psplus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.playstation.com%2F%23%21%2Fzh-hant-hk%2Fhome%2F%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%2588%25B2%2Fpsplus&d=%2FlPv3t7WlvhdxvNzqqPsTleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=9f089d8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.playstation.com/#!/zh-hant-hk/home/%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2/psplus</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://asia.playstation.com/hk/cht/psn/psPlus#currentOffers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.playstation.com%2Fhk%2Fcht%2Fpsn%2FpsPlus%23currentOffers&d=%2FlPv3t7WlvhdxvNzqqPsTleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=5205e8b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://asia.playstation.com/hk/cht/psn/psPlus#currentOffers</a><br />\n <br />\n**(就算未有PS3，PSVita，PS4，只可一日擁有PS Plus，你都可以用上面網頁預先下載)<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q5.</span> PS Plus會藉可否累積上去？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A5.</span> 可以，例子：你會藉到下一年一月完，你在本年五月購買多次12個月會藉，會藉完結日期會由下一年一月增加12個月到後一年一月。<br />\n**(用信用卡續會請緊記要自行取消自動續約，並且建議所有玩家使用雙重認證。)<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q6.</span> 有咩GAME玩？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A6.</span> 下面各大網頁都有game list<br />\n中文Source:<br />\n巴哈姆特 Playstation 4 討論區<br />\n2014年<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60596&amp;snA=512&amp;tnum=36\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D60596%26snA%3D512%26tnum%3D36&d=%2FlPv3t7WlvhdxvNzqqPsTleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=e3bfe363\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60596&amp;snA=512&amp;tnum=36</a><br />\n2015年<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60596&amp;snA=9802&amp;tnum=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D60596%26snA%3D9802%26tnum%3D2&d=%2FlPv3t7WlvhdxvNzqqPsTleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=72b00b83\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60596&amp;snA=9802&amp;tnum=2</a><br />\n2016年<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60596&amp;snA=18557&amp;tnum=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D60596%26snA%3D18557%26tnum%3D2&d=%2FlPv3t7WlvhdxvNzqqPsTleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=c9686b18\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60596&amp;snA=18557&amp;tnum=2</a><br />\n2017年<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60596&amp;snA=28525&amp;tnum=22\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D60596%26snA%3D28525%26tnum%3D22&d=%2FlPv3t7WlvhdxvNzqqPsTleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=bd8c6b92\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60596&amp;snA=28525&amp;tnum=22</a><br />\n英文sources<br />\nWikipedia:<br />\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_PlayStation_4_games\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FList_of_PlayStation_4_games&d=%2FlPv3t7WlvhdxvNzqqPsTleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=a9deda92\" target=\"_blank\">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_PlayStation_4_games</a><br />\nIGN (US) <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ign.com/ps4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ign.com%2Fps4&d=%2FlPv3t7WlvhdxvNzqqPsTleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=e50f3b81\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ign.com/ps4</a><br />\n其他網頁<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.polygon.com/ps4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.polygon.com%2Fps4&d=%2FlPv3t7WlvhdxvNzqqPsTleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=464e6b5e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.polygon.com/ps4</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eurogamer.net/?platform=PS4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eurogamer.net%2F%3Fplatform%3DPS4&d=%2FlPv3t7WlvhdxvNzqqPsTleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=ff3cf606\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eurogamer.net/?platform=PS4</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.computerandvideogames.com/homepage.php?channel=playstation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.computerandvideogames.com%2Fhomepage.php%3Fchannel%3Dplaystation&d=%2FlPv3t7WlvhdxvNzqqPsTleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=aa116dbc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.computerandvideogames.com/homepage.php?channel=playstation</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.joystiq.com/ps4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.joystiq.com%2Fps4%2F&d=%2FlPv3t7WlvhdxvNzqqPsTleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=99a50bd2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.joystiq.com/ps4/</a><br />\n日版sources<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.famitsu.com/schedule/ps4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.famitsu.com%2Fschedule%2Fps4%2F&d=%2FlPv3t7WlvhdxvNzqqPsTleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=cc558739\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.famitsu.com/schedule/ps4/</a>"},{"pid":"d8d9e457bda8afd6be6be896770c0c4a540f889f","tid":338668,"uid":11402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T11:15:31.000Z","msg":"<em>CUH-11XX系列PS4</em>：內部電子部件小改進，機能與CUH-10XX系列相同（同樣有彈碟問題，解決方法同上）<br />\n<em>CUH-12XX系列PS4</em>：以實體開機出碟按鈕取代易出現彈碟問題的舊輕觸式按鈕，小量減重及降低耗電量和噪音。<br />\n以上3款系列，尺寸同樣為約305 x 275 &times; 53 mm，機能三者大致相同，並已停產<br />\n <br />\n詳細對比請到下方網站觀看：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.playstation.com/en-gb/explore/ps4/tech-specs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.playstation.com%2Fen-gb%2Fexplore%2Fps4%2Ftech-specs%2F&d=%2FlPv3t7WlvhdxvNzqqPsTleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=969260c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.playstation.com/en-gb/explore/ps4/tech-specs/</a><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>官方主要配件簡介：</strong></span><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無線控制器Dualshock&reg;4：</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6J21Nin.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6J21Nin.jpg&h=255cc275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E2n4Ecr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE2n4Ecr.jpg&h=5d5915c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCUH-ZCT2：新款，可用無線連接或USB連接，更人性化地加入正面Touchpad加LED燈顯示，外觀及手感與初代有出入<br />\n <br />\n官方建議售價：398港元<br />\n <br />\n初代有多款顏色及特別款式可供選擇，新款暫時得黑、白、銀(水貨)、迷彩(水貨)、紅及藍六色<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/18JSE8D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F18JSE8D.jpg&h=45b8a9d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pnT5710.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpnT5710.jpg&h=1b2c49f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCUH-ZCT1：初代，只能用無線連接，USB只作充電用途<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">動態控制器PlayStation&reg;Move：</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C16ZvGr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC16ZvGr.gif&h=158fc8a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCECH-ZCM1G Y：可配合PSVR及PS Camera使用進行VR遊戲(非必要)<br />\n <br />\n官方建議售價：298港元<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">PS VR專用射擊控制器PlayStation&reg;VR Aim Controller：</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8W6K0m1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8W6K0m1.jpg&h=3b0d6514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n官方建議售價：468港元 (2017年5月16日（二）推出)<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">攝影機PlayStation&reg;Camera：</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FA2oGAy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFA2oGAy.gif&h=d8a28aba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCUH-ZEY2 G：新款圓柱型連底座直立支撐架，機能及用途與舊款相同；支撐架可自由調整攝影機角度外，亦便於放置在電視機等各種平台上。"},{"pid":"b4be25ff26a54707e7ea548a7ffdd0e0b77de73b","tid":338668,"uid":11402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T11:16:07.000Z","msg":"官方建議售價：398港元<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/24wJTiM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F24wJTiM.gif&h=2786ddd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCUH-ZEY1 G：舊款方體型無底座，可單純用作直播時拍攝玩家，或遊玩動感遊戲，亦可以配合PSVR進行VR遊戲(必要)<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">虛擬現實裝置PlayStation&reg;VR：</span><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7NF8K6D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7NF8K6D.jpg&h=079ff6e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPSVR頭戴眼鏡<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h26L7z1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh26L7z1.png&h=7101ee98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n實際整套PSVR<br />\n <br />\nCUH-ZVR1 H：需配合PS Camera進行遊戲(必需)，部份遊戲需PS Move方可遊玩，可作2D戲院式遊玩或3DVR式遊玩，更新主機更新Firmware至4.5 Version後更支援3D播放<br />\n <br />\n於2016年10月13日正式推出，官方建議售價：3,180港元(淨PSVR)，3,480港元(連PS Camera)，3,980港元(LOG-ON限定，連PS Camera及2個PS Move)<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">需留意官方建議遊玩空間</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/342n01Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F342n01Y.jpg&h=a4a9f9ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n詳細PSVR介紹可上PSVR官方查閱：<br />\n<a href=\"https://asia.playstation.com/hk/cht/psvr/main\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.playstation.com%2Fhk%2Fcht%2Fpsvr%2Fmain&d=%2FlPv3t7WlvhdxvNzqqPsTleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=44309c06\" target=\"_blank\">https://asia.playstation.com/hk/cht/psvr/main</a><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">直立架Vertical Stand</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O6P3G12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO6P3G12.jpg&h=ea382e74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCUH-ZST1：<span style=\"color: red;\">只適用於CUH-1XXX系列PS4</span>直立擺放時使用(非必要但個人建議)<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/75tjS2p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F75tjS2p.jpg&h=ea703428&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCUH-ZST2：<span style=\"color: red;\">只適用於CUH-2XXX系列PS4 Slim及CUH-7XXX系列PS4 Pro</span>直立擺放時使用(非必要但個人建議)<br />\n <br />\n官方建議售價：168港元<br />\n <br />\n <br />\nInitial template was provided by 貓之子 and completed by 蒼月A<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/11yn_Rtpv3JdoO4gnyF1NrjhTpgjiHyyD-tyNIzDJED8/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F11yn_Rtpv3JdoO4gnyF1NrjhTpgjiHyyD-tyNIzDJED8%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=%2FlPv3t7WlvhdxvNzqqPsTleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=41ff69bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/11yn_Rtpv3JdoO4gnyF1NrjhTpgjiHyyD-tyNIzDJED8/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n <br />\n本文內容只限Lihkg的PS4機主使用，其他網頁轉載必定追究"},{"pid":"a5b59bbe226777db3b857dfb7fb7bdbba08527ea","tid":338668,"uid":11402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T11:16:52.000Z","msg":"推爆左冇人開po既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出左街用手機好難開po"},{"pid":"a8ee46be671c5880fc8b96aa498c3f6886971544","tid":338668,"uid":5020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T11:20:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推爆左冇人開po既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出左街用手機好難開po</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n二石四鳥巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"657871be6d8a4ae2f19cce9233a02e3d0aceb21e","tid":33866